snippet.title: PAC-MAN comes to Minecraft!
snippet.description: The legendary arcade classic PAC-MAN turns 40 and celebrates by coming  to Minecraft! WAKA-WAKA your way through a-mazeing 3D maze madness! Find out more at https://minecraft.net/article/happy-40th-birthday--pac-man- and join the fun: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/pdp/?id=366e895b-d090-4151-a83a-e86c6b339732
